        {
            "title": "中國九月新增近三百萬股民",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>上交所公布今年9月份內地證券戶口新增開戶數目為293.72萬戶，按月增速加快至10.83%，按年更激增60.73%，開戶人數是今年3月以來最多。累計今年首9個月，A股新開戶數目達到2014.89萬戶，較去年同期升49.64%。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>首三季累添2014萬戶</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單計A股個人投資者，9月份新增開戶數目為292.63萬，是去年10月以來最多。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">回顧去年9月內地「政策組合拳」刺激A股反彈，帶動去年10月份A股個人投資者新增開戶數目達到683.97萬個，今年9月的個人投資者A股開戶數目僅及當月四成，反映散戶現時熱度仍低於去年。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-515e44aa-ab0e-343b-9e03-22a22c444d1f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，內地傳媒《中國基金報》報道，俗稱「兩融」（孖展借貸和借貨沽空）的賬戶開戶數目，自8月以來已經超出去年同期，刺激內地券商紛紛上調融資類業務規模上限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報今年最少有5間內地券商先後上調融資類業務規模上限，最新一間是浙商證券。事實上，A股兩融餘額自今年9月初開始反覆刷新歷史高位，最新10月9日數據顯示，兩融餘額錄2.45萬億元人民幣。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%89%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E8%82%A1%E6%B0%91-183500559.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-11 02:40:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國股指期貨微漲 高估值憂慮依然不散",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DarhdIg4pEeei3uE4sTgcg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/77690d46476f7e68b008c6ae056aa9bd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 周末臨近，股市稍作喘息，本周在市場對全球股市凌冽漲勢是否可持續的猜測下，市場走勢震盪。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紐約時間8:20，標普500指數期貨上漲0.1%，該指數早前兩次收創紀錄，隨後一日稍有回撤，本周有望溫和收高。那斯達克100指數和道指期貨上漲0.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾在盤前交易中上漲，此前這家獲美國政府支持的晶片製造商推出了新產品。高通股價下跌，因中國對其收購Autotalks交易啟動反托辣斯調查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Pepperstone集團高級研究策略師Michael Brown表示：「在經濟基本面強勁、企業盈利成長穩健及聯儲會政策趨松的背景下，股市回調仍應視為買入良機，當前阻力最小的路徑仍是上行。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8594f1a9-75f9-3b4a-a8af-c8f93c26218e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_InbXA_eKZkmZYVcCewm7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/eff859f5f71502ae56695e485d300df6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bank J Safra Sarasin的股票策略師Wolf von Rotberg指出，儘管科技股引領了標普500指數的反彈，但電氣設備製造商和建築公司等其他行業也受益於人工智能支出，使漲勢更趨廣泛。但他指出，基於預估本益比計算，該基準指數當前估值已達近25年來最高水平，估值過高，令人不安。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Von Rotberg表示：「儘管近期人工智能主題未受干擾，但我們建議投資者在經歷如此強勁反彈且估值居高之際，應謹慎避免追漲。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Stock Futures Drift Amid Valuation Concerns: Markets Wrap</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Anand Krishnamoorthy、Jan-Patrick Barnert.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%BE%AE%E6%BC%B2-%E9%AB%98%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A3-130842401.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 21:45:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "銷售旺季伊始 特斯拉上海工廠出貨量上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"581\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9aYZnuPd0eNZmTZdhUlc5Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6037f12130adbf965fd79d5dc89f47cc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著中國汽車市場迎來銷售旺季，汽車製造商開始為完成年度目標做最後衝刺，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特斯拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特斯拉\">特斯拉</a>上海工廠9月份的出貨量有所成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國乘聯分會公佈的初步數據顯示，該車企上月從該工廠交付90,812輛汽車，同比成長2.8%。雖然數據未區分出口與國內銷售，但這些車輛大部分將交付給中國客戶。這標志著今年下滑趨勢的緩解 —— 特斯拉上海工廠今年九個月中有七個月的躉售銷量出現下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國市場的強勁表現助力特斯拉創下驚艷的第三季度業績。上周該公司公佈全球交付量再創紀錄，因美國消費者爭相在9月30日稅收優惠到期前搶購電動汽車。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b4ded9d7-504f-33ed-a170-6ab14435cefc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"581\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NiksA0zmynpbNZJk7MHf_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f20b0365c5d11e653d9b7dc679942db8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管特斯拉能否延續在美國市場的銷售勢頭尚不明朗，但其在中國9月份的強勁銷量數據表明，對第四季度需求持樂觀態度。10月初的黃金周假期將成為衡量全年餘下時間銷量的風向球。這家由馬斯克領導的企業還開始交付六座Model Y運動型多功能車，以吸引更多注重家庭使用的消費者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，中國最暢銷汽車品牌比亞迪9月銷量同比下滑，這是該公司逾18個月來的首次月度銷量下滑。不過，這家總部設在深圳的製造商在純電動汽車市場已連續四個季度超越特斯拉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Tesla’s China Shipments Rise at Start of Busy Sales Season</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Vlad Savov.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%97%BA%E5%AD%A3%E4%BC%8A%E5%A7%8B-%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%A8%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-132208986.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 23:25:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事Waller稱過去幾個月就業人數恐負成長 希望繼續降息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會理事Christopher Waller表示，過去幾個月就業成長可能為負，勞動力市場已成為他最大的憂慮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「過去幾個月就業成長很可能為負，「Waller周五接受CNBC採訪時稱。「勞動力市場疲軟，這是政策制定的關鍵所在，是我們需要知道的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原定上周發布的9月非農報告因政府停擺而推遲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國政府停擺仍看不到結束的曙光 初步經濟影響逐漸顯現</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Waller於2020年由川普任命，是接替傑羅姆·鮑威爾成為下任主席的熱門人選 —— 鮑威爾的主席任期將於明年5月屆滿。Waller表示面試進展順利，進行了嚴肅的經濟討論。他還表示，面試不涉及政治。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-04c424a3-92f7-3a33-a8e2-42b8ec5b23e3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，希望繼續降息，但強調決策者應保持謹慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Waller Says Fed Chair Interview Went Well, Labor Market Is Weak</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8Bwaller%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%81%90%E8%B2%A0%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-122843306.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 21:00:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "加拿大9月份就業人數增加60,400人 失業率持穩於7.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 加拿大9月新增就業人數超出預期，但由於更多人進入勞動力市場，失業率持穩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加拿大統計局周五公佈的數據顯示，9月份就業增加6.04萬人，主要由全職崗位成長拉動。失業率維持在7.1%不變。就業增幅甚至超過了彭博對經濟學家的調查中的最樂觀預測，該調查的中值預期為新增5,000個崗位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">成長主要由公共部門就業領銜。製造業新增2.78萬名從業者，農業、醫療健保及其他服務業也都有所增員。就業率，即工作年齡人口中的就業比例，在9月份上升0.1個百分點至60.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-10ae15b3-99b4-39de-8a51-076d1c89d963-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出人意料的強勁就業成長表明，加拿大勞動力市場在與美國的關稅爭端中表現出一定韌性。工廠就業躍升——儘管並非由汽車行業推動，表明該部門可能受益於《美墨加協定》下部分產品獲得的關稅豁免。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告也可能提振市場對加拿大央行在10月29日下一次利率決議上按兵不動的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，這一好於預期的增幅僅部分對沖了7月和8月的重大崗位流失。過去三個月，加拿大經濟淨減4.59萬個崗位，為疫情以來最疲弱的季度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Canada Employment Rises 60,400, Jobless Rate Sticks at 7.1%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mario Baker Ramirez.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A79%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BD%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A060-400%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E6%8C%81%E7%A9%A9%E6%96%BC7-1-130219573.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 21:45:47",
